name: Rebirth of the Protoss Map 3 - Pest Control
shortName: Rebirth of the Protoss Map 3 - Pest Control
description:
This is the 3rd map of my campaign
\-------------- THE REBIRTH OF THE PROTOSS --------------------
The campaign takes place in a time will Raynor and his friends tries to build up a
fleet against the Zerg. Exactly at that time you pass planet Haven your fleet was attacked and destroyed
by a Protoss armada. Since now their are 3 Maps finished and the 4th will follow in a few days.
Only Map 1 is released on Battle net, the others are only downloadable over
some Starcraft 2 Map/Fan-Sites. To start it, doubleklick on the map (load map in editor) and than klick "test/start map".
All Difficulties can be set at mapstart.
